# Shared environment variables for every workflow that needs them.
# Each top-level workflow's first job step (after `actions/checkout`)
# loads this file with `cat .github/env >> "$GITHUB_ENV"`. The format
# is `KEY=VALUE` per line (no shell quoting / interpolation) which is
# what `$GITHUB_ENV` consumes verbatim.
#
# Bump `MISE_VERSION` here to upgrade every workflow's mise install in
# a single edit. Lockstep with `mise.toml`'s tooling pins.
MISE_VERSION=v2026.5.10
